Name | Type | Description|
---- | ---- | -----------
| **guid** | _uuid_ | Unique identifier for the role. |
| **created_at** | _datetime_ | The time with zone when the role was created.|
| **updated_at**  | _datetime_ | The time with zone when the role was last updated. |
| **apps.per_process_memory_in_mb** | _integer_ | Maximum memory a single process or task can use. |
| **apps.total_instances** | _integer_ | Total instances all the started processes in an organization can have. |
| **apps.per_app_tasks** | _integer_ | Maximum number of running tasks a single application can have. |
| **services.paid_services_allowed** | _boolean_ | If instances of paid service plans can be created. |
| **services.total_service_instances** | _integer_ | Total number of service instances that an organization can have. |
| **services.total_service_keys** | _integer_ | Total number of service keys that an organization can have. |
| **routes.total_routes** | _integer_ | Total number of routes that an organization can have. |
| **routes.total_reserved_ports** | _integer_ | Total number of ports that all routes in an organization can reserve. |
| **domains.total_domains** | _integer_ | Total number of domains that can be scoped to an organization. |
| **relationships.organizations** | [_to-many relationship_](#to-many-relationships) | A relationship to the organizations the quota applies to. |
| **links** | [_links object_](#links) | Links to related resources. |
